# Template/Starter code for React Components

## Quick copy

```tsx
import './_COMPONENT_NAME_.css';

export interface Props {}

/**
 *
 */
export function ComponentName(props: Props) {
  return <>ComponentName</>;
}

export default ComponentName;
```
